{"tid":996182,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【令人不安】指控MJ孌童紀錄片曝光 受害人現身首映禮","createTime":"2019-01-26T05:39:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-27T14:39:40.000Z","uid":119223,"like":5,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f2e56c8f8acac55649d0d739735e036d70ef5c00","tid":996182,"uid":119223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T05:39:04.000Z","msg":"已故流行天王米高積遜（Michael Jackson）生前曾被指性侵兒童，他死後多年一部關於MJ事蹟的紀錄片《Leaving Neverland》昨日於美國辛丹斯電影節（Sundance Film Festival）放映，片中訪問了童年時被MJ性侵的兩名男子排舞師Wade Robson與James Safechuck，兩人亦有現身記錄片的首映禮。<br />\n<br />\n紀錄片《Leaving Neverland》長達四小時分為兩部份，首部份講兩人被性侵經歷，James Safechuck談MJ如何於性侵他之前取得其家信任，James詳細講被性侵過程，又提到MJ於完事後會給予他們珠寶。Wade Robson則表示於跳舞比賽認識MJ，他與James同樣指MJ會教他們保密，而樂園Nerverland亦設有警報，當有人到訪時他們便要穿回衣服。兩人亦指年紀漸大遭性侵越來越嚴重，他們會被要求睇鹹片，以及開始肛交。受害人母親亦有受訪，她們提到開始時如何信任MJ，又指MJ講過最喜愛的男孩是麥哥利高堅（Macaulay Culkin）。<br />\n。<br />\n紀錄片第二部份則講到2003年於MJ孌童案爆出後的情況，兩人指MJ分別要求他們做證，James表示他拒絕後，MJ亦與他斷絕聯絡，Wade則說因太驚而為MJ辯護。兩名受害人首映期間接受觀眾提問，Wade一度爆喊，全場觀眾更向他們站立致意。看了紀錄片的外國傳媒形容影片令人不安，而不少觀眾於看畢後都於Twitter留言，最多人用了「令人震驚的」字眼看形容。"},{"pid":"9d141cc32f2fabbc14299b79bc1327b30bd22715","tid":996182,"uid":119223,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T05:40:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190126/large/1548479611_652a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190126%2Flarge%2F1548479611_652a.jpg&h=4f6f6f3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n導演Dan Hall（左起）、James Safechuck與Wade Robson現身首映禮<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190126/large/1548479615_df5c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190126%2Flarge%2F1548479615_df5c.jpg&h=db6336b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nWade指被MJ性侵長達七年<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190126/large/1548479601_26dd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190126%2Flarge%2F1548479601_26dd.jpg&h=c0267053&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nMJ事蹟的紀錄片《Leaving Neverland》昨日於美國辛丹斯電影節放映　"},{"pid":"cff478cae79744d5d1d330ae185c30143c0b183a","tid":996182,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T05:40:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4daa6a6dae8824e9b0aaf51e365c5938aec0c3b8","tid":996182,"uid":122264,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T05:41:47.000Z","msg":"死左你講咩都得架啦"},{"pid":"666483eae2bbb13fd2fc071901b4cb22d74cc215","tid":996182,"uid":46911,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"4daa6a6dae8824e9b0aaf51e365c5938aec0c3b8","tid":996182,"uid":122264,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T05:41:47.000Z","msg":"死左你講咩都得架啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T05:58:02.000Z","msg":"死左都仲要比人metoo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1685906599962784d905273dd313d5794494677b","tid":996182,"uid":55309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T06:07:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bfaafb426fd511d339e08d73e762bc62b444796","tid":996182,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T06:09:43.000Z","msg":"好彩有metoo運動提返呢件事"},{"pid":"7b6033cd1470d715df5a738b2d7d99658998a619","tid":996182,"uid":157362,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T06:11:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a05e8e07917d9fda12004d7c4d7c2b3aa4b746b5","tid":996182,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T06:15:33.000Z","msg":"唔係判咗無罪？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/